ight:21px;background-color:#FFFFFF;color:#404040;\">鼻敏感, 气管敏感皮肤敏感养颜袪班</span><br /><span style=\"font-family:tahoma, arial, \'宋体\', sans-serif;line-height:21px;background-color:#FFFFFF;color:#404040;\">胃炎, 胃溃疡, 前列腺炎, 妇科病哮喘, 感冒</span><br /><span style=\"font-family:tahoma, arial, \'宋体\', sans-serif;line-height:21px;background-color:#FFFFFF;color:#404040;\">免疫系统失调, 肝炎, 便秘, 痔疮等</span><br /><span style=\"font-family:tahoma, arial, \'宋体\', sans-serif;line-height:21px;background-color:#FFFFFF;color:#404040;\">共能舒缓化疗及放疗引起的副作用</span><br /><br /><span style=\"font-family:tahoma, arial, \'宋体\', sans-serif;line-height:21px;background-color:#FFFFFF;color:#404040;\">主要成份</span><br /><span style=\"font-family:tahoma, arial, \'宋体\', sans-serif;line-height:21px;background-color:#FFFFFF;color:#404040;\">Bee Propoils 500mg, Zinc Gluconate, Ascorbic Acid, Beta Carotene, Soybean Oil,</span><br /><span style=\"font-family:tahoma, arial, \'宋体\', sans-serif;line-height:21px;background-color:#FFFFFF;color:#404040;\">Cocount Oil, Beeswax</span><br /><br /><span style=\"font-family:tahoma, arial, \'宋体\', sans-serif;line-height:21px;background-color:#FFFFFF;color:#404040;\">用法</span><br /><span style=\"font-family:tahoma, arial, \'宋体\', sans-serif;line-height:21px;background-color:#FFFFFF;color:#404040;\">每日一至三次, 每次一粒连服90至180天</span><br /><span style=\"font-family:tahoma, arial, \'宋体\', sans-serif;line-height:21px;background-color:#FFFFFF;color:#404040;\">患者应按耐心服药直至疗程完毕</span><br /><br /><span style=\"font-family:tahoma, arial, \'宋体\', sans-serif;line-height:21px;background-color:#FFFFFF;color:#404040;\">规格</span><br /><span style=\"font-family:tahoma, arial, \'宋体\', sans-serif;line-height:21px;background-color:#FFFFFF;color:#404040;\">90粒</span><br /><br /><span style=\"font-family:tahoma, arial, \'宋体\', sans-serif;line-height:21px;background-color:#FFFFFF;color:#404040;\">产地</span><br /><span style=\"font-family:tahoma, arial, \'宋体\', sans-serif;line-height:21px;background-color:#FFFFFF;colo