次2瓶，一日1-2次。葡萄糖六磷酸去氫酵素（G6PD）缺乏症患者避免服用。</span></span></span>\n</p>\n<p style=\"font-family:tahoma, arial, \'宋体\', sans-serif;font-size:14px;background-color:#FFFFFF;color:#404040;\">\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:\'microsoft yahei\';font-size:14px;\"><strong><span style=\"color:#FF00FF;font-size:14px;\">獲註冊證明</span></strong></span></span>\n</p>\n<p style=\"font-family:tahoma, arial, \'宋体\', sans-serif;font-size:14px;background-color:#FFFFFF;color:#404040;\">\n	<span style=\"font-size:18px;\"><span style=\"font-family:\'microsoft yahei\';\"><span style=\"color:#000000;font-size:14px;\">猴棗，又名猴丹、猴子棗，提煉自結石，自古用於小兒保健，具</span><strong><u><span style=\"color:#FF00FF;font-size:14px;\">清熱鎮驚、豁痰定喘、解毒消腫之效</span></u></strong><span style=\"color:#000000;font-size:14px;\">。小兒經常有久咳、久喘、痰多、夜睡不寧等問題。寶寶不懂把痰吐出，如患咳嗽往往復原較慢、很難根治。猴棗散可化痰止咳、清宿痰平肺喘，定驚安神，更可清小兒胎毒積熱，治口咽腫痛，可用於預防以及改善風热症狀。</span></span></span>\n</p>\n<p style=\"font-family:tahoma, arial, \'宋体\', sans-serif;font-size:14px;background-color:#FFFFFF;color:#404040;\">\n	<span style=\"font-size:18px;\"><span style=\"font-family:\'microsoft yahei\';\"><span style=\"color:#000000;font-size:14px;\">「衍生精製猴棗散」於市面已推出多年，最近重新推出升級版，是</span><strong><span style=\"color:#FF00FF;font-size:14px;\">首個成功獲得中成藥註冊證明書及</span></strong><strong><span style=\"color:#FF00FF;font-size:14px;\">HKC</span></strong><strong><span style=\"color:#FF00FF;font-size:14px;\">編號的猴棗散產品</span></strong><span style=\"color:#000000;font-size:14px;\">，品質符合本港中醫藥規管。所以購買時，要留意產品包裝上是否附有註冊編號，並列明主治及功能，保證是正貨。</span><span style=\"background-color:#FFFF00;color:#0000FF;\"></span></span></span>\n</p>\n<p style=\"font-family:tahoma, arial, \'宋体\', sans-serif;font-size:14px;background-color:#FFFFFF;color:#404040;\">\n	<span style=\"font-size:18px;\"><span style=\"font-family:\'microsoft yahei\';\"><span style=\"color:#FF0000;font-size:14px;\">注意事项：</span><span style=\"color:#000000;font-size:14px;\">忌食生冷，油膩燥熱之物，長期病患者服用前，應咨詢醫生意見。</span></span></span>\n</p>','','','衍生精製猴棗散','0.00','0','千克','0','2','0','99','','0','0','0','0' ); 
INSERT INTO `iwebshop_goods` VALUES( '126','衍生至尊感冒止咳顆粒沖劑','SD139487202498','0','38.00','40.00','0.00','2014-03-15 16:28:22','','2014-03-15 16:28:22','100','upload/2014/03/15/20140315042737204.jpg','0','<p align=\"left\" style=\"font-family:tahoma, arial, \'宋体\', sans-serif;font-size:14px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\n	<span style=\"color:#CC0000;\"><span>主治】：用于外感风热所致的感冒，症见发热恶风.头痛鼻塞.咽喉肿痛.咳嗽.周身不适</span></span>\n</p>\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"font-family:tahoma, arial, \'宋体\', sans-serif;font-size:14px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\n	<span style=\"color:#CC0000;\"><span>【成分】：每10g浓缩颗粒中含有</span></span>\n</p>\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"font-family:tahoma, arial, \'宋体\', sans-serif;font-size:14px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\n	<span style=\"color:#CC0000;\"><span>葛根（1.00g），柴胡（1.00g），山银花（0.75g），青蒿（0.75g），连翘（0.75g），黄芪（0.75g），苦杏仁（0.50g），桔梗（0.50g），薄荷脑（0.0015g）</span></span>\n</p>\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"font-family:tahoma, arial, \'宋体\', sans-serif;font-size:14px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\n	<span style=\"color:#CC0000;\"><span>【饮用方法及分量】：每日3次，每次1包；用適量溫水開調飲用。</span></span>\n</p>\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"font-family:tahoma, arial, \'宋体\', sans-serif;font-size:14px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\n	<span style=\"color:#CC0000;\"><span>【储存方式】：放置於陰涼乾爽及孩童不能觸及的地方，避免誤服。</span></span>\n</p>\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"font-family:tahoma, arial, \'宋体\', sans-serif;font-size:14px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\n	<span style=\"color:#CC0000;\"><span>【注意事项】：一：本品清热解表，止咳化痰，外感风寒者慎用。</span></span>\n</p>\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"font-family:tahoma, arial, \'宋体\', sans-serif;font-size:14px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\n	<span style=\"color:#CC0000;\"><span>                       二：服药期间饮食宜清淡，忌食辛辣油腻之品，以免助火生痰</span></span>\n</p>\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"font-family:tahoma, arial, \'宋体\', sans-serif;font-size:14px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\n	<span style=\"color:#CC0000;\"><span>                       三：开调后未经饮用，请存放于雪柜内，并在开调后24小时内饮用。</span></span>\n</p>\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"font-family:tahoma, arial, \'宋体\', sans-serif;font-size:14px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\n	<span style=\"color:#CC0000;\"><span>                       四：如出现敏感或者不适症状，请立即停止服用并且咨询您的医生。</span></span>\n</p>','','','衍生至尊感冒止咳顆粒沖劑','0.00','0','千克','0','1','0','99','','0','0','0','0' ); 
